function.description: Returns the length of the given list or object.

example.title: Usage
example.code:
use Collection, System;
var list = ["a","b","c","d","e"]; //list with five elements System.print(Collection.length(list)); // 5 var object = {1:"a",2:"b",3:"c"}; //object with three elements System.print(Collection.length(object)); // 3
